log\n\nJanuary 26, 2026\n\nSub-Hourly STF Improves Day-Ahead Positioning in the Era of Renewables\n\nBlog\n\nJanuary 26, 2026\n\nBehind PJM’s 800% Increase in Capacity Prices and Trump’s Emergency Auction Plan\n\nBlog\n\nJanuary 8, 2026\n\nGermany Proves Transmission is Just as Critical ",
