arkets, \ndifferent bid validation rule triggered and resulted in unintended loss of high \npriority status for some exports\n– CAISO is assessing enhancements to the validation rules and an \nimplementation date will be provided once determined\nCAISO PUBLIC\nPrice Formation Enhancements –\nRules for Bidding Above the Soft Offer Cap\n",
